---
title: Strike48 Labs
description: Documentation for the Strike48 security platform
layout: false
templateEngine: njk
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <title>Strike48 Labs</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/landing.css">
  <style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap");
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif; color: #0f172a; background: #fff; }
    .neural-graph[data-mode="hero"] {
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cookie-banner { position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 9999; background: #1e293b; border-top: 1px solid #334155; box-shadow: 0 -4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; animation: cookie-slide-up 0.4s ease; }
    .cookie-banner[data-hidden] { display: none; }
    @keyframes cookie-slide-up { from { transform: translateY(100%); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } }
    .cookie-inner { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .cookie-text { color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 0.8125rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cookie-text a { color: #60a5fa; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
    .cookie-text a:hover { color: #93bbfd; }
    .cookie-text-small { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cookie-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .cookie-btn { padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: background-color 0.15s ease; }
    .cookie-btn-accept { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
    .cookie-btn-accept:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .cookie-btn-decline { background: transparent; color: #cbd5e1; border: 1px solid #475569; }
    .cookie-btn-decline:hover { border-color: #64748b; color: #f1f5f9; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Cookie Consent -->
  <div id="cookie-banner" class="cookie-banner" role="dialog" aria-label="Cookie consent">
    <div class="cookie-inner">
      <p class="cookie-text">
        This website stores cookies on your computer to collect information about how you interact with our website. We use this information to customize content and analyze traffic. See our <a href="/legal/privacy-policy/">Cookie Policy</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="cookie-text cookie-text-small">
        If you decline, your information won't be tracked. A single cookie will remember your preference.
      </p>
      <div class="cookie-actions">
        <button id="cookie-accept" class="cookie-btn cookie-btn-accept">Accept</button>
        <button id="cookie-decline" class="cookie-btn cookie-btn-decline">Decline</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="landing-hero" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <canvas class="neural-graph" data-mode="hero"></canvas>
    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      <img src="/assets/img/strike48-logo-light.svg" alt="Strike48" height="48" style="margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; display: block;">
      <p class="tagline">Documentation for the Strike48 security platform. Desktop connector apps for end users, and SDKs for building custom tools and connectors.</p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="/strikehub/getting-started/" class="cta-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="/overview/" class="cta-secondary">Read the Docs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Products: End Users -->
  <section class="products-section">
    <h2>For End Users</h2>
    <div class="products-grid">
      <a href="/prospector-studio/" class="product-card">
        <h3>Prospector Studio</h3>
        <p>AI-powered workflow automation and agent platform.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/strikehub/" class="product-card">
        <h3>StrikeHub</h3>
        <p>The unified desktop shell.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/kubestudio/" class="product-card">
        <h3>KubeStudio</h3>
        <p>Kubernetes cluster management dashboard.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/pick/" class="product-card">
        <h3>Pick</h3>
        <p>Headless penetration testing toolkit.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/developers/strikekit/" class="product-card">
        <h3>StrikeKit</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive red team operations workstation.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Products: Developers -->
  <section class="products-section">
    <h2>For Developers</h2>
    <div class="products-grid">
      <a href="/developers/prospector-studio/graphql-api/" class="product-card">
        <h3>Prospector Studio API</h3>
        <p>GraphQL API reference for integrators and connector developers.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/developers/sdk-rs/" class="product-card">
        <h3>SDK for Rust</h3>
        <p>Build powerful, type-safe connectors with the Strike48 SDK.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <h2>Built for Increasing Productivity</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F50C;</div>
        <h3>Connector Architecture</h3>
        <p>Modular connector system — each tool runs as an isolated process with its own UI, communicating over IPC.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F512;</div>
        <h3>Secure by Default</h3>
        <p>Unix domain sockets for process isolation. OIDC authentication with automatic token injection. No ports exposed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x26A1;</div>
        <h3>Native Performance</h3>
        <p>Built with Rust and Dioxus for sub-2-second startup. WebView rendering with minimal memory overhead.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F5D4;</div>
        <h3>Single Window</h3>
        <p>All your Strike48 connectors in one native window. Switch between tools without alt-tabbing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x2728;</div>
        <h3>AI-Powered</h3>
        <p>Autonomous agents, RAG-enabled knowledge bases, and multi-step workflows — automate reconnaissance, analysis, and reporting with AI.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
    <p>Set up StrikeHub and start managing your connector apps in one place.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="/strikehub/getting-started/" class="cta-primary">Quick Start Guide</a>
      <a href="/overview/" class="cta-secondary">Browse Documentation</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="/assets/js/neural-graph.js"></script>
  <script src="/assets/js/cookie-consent.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
